ComicInfo.Title: Supernature Summit - Part Four of the Gathering
ComicInfo.Summary:
Superhumans from all over the world have gone missing, which causes some concern, as the Oblivion spheres were just sent once again towards Earth.
Meanwhile Tommy addresses the Super Nation and lays out the rules. The various members meet each other, take part in the banquet, and get their workshop assignments. Ratman gets turned down by every girl he comes on to and Morningstar finally gets her revenge against Shapeshifter.
